Introduction

<App>Apps ("We," "us," or "our") values the privacy of our users ("you"). This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle the personal information we collect from you when you use our mobile application (the "App"). Please review this Privacy Policy carefully to understand how we protect your privacy. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated by posting the updated policy on the App or our website, and through other appropriate communication channels. Your continued use of the App after any changes indicates your acceptance of the new terms.

