2、Introduction and purpose of this Privacy Notice

We, the above-named controller (“<App>”, "We," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting personal data concerning you, and respecting your privacy.

When you use our products and services, including websites such as <domain>, or mobile apps, we will process certain personal data that concerns you.  ‘Process’ or ‘processing’ as used in this Privacy Notice includes any operation performed on personal data or on sets of personal data, like collection, storage, organisation, retrieval, updating, amending, deletion, consultation, use, sharing or making available internally or to others.

This Website and App Users Website Privacy Notice (“Privacy Notice”) sets out details of the processing we carry out, the purpose of the processing, the legal basis for the processing, our legal obligations as controller, and your rights in relation to that processing.

3、Personal data we may collect from you and how we process it

If you visit one of our websites, including  <domain>
- IP Address
We will process this information in order to:
- Give you access to the website
- Enhance your experience
- Improve the experience of all our users.

See also the information on cookies below and the cookie policy and cookie consent on the relevant website.
 
If you use one of our mobile apps
All the above information plus:
- Apple or Google User ID
- Specific user behaviour characteristics
- Preferences including advertising preferences
- Technical device data, device and website usage data.
- the name you have associated with your device
- your country
- your specific geolocation
- information about <App> and other third-party apps you have on your device
- a <App> player ID number that is created by <App> and used to identify you

We will process this information in order to:
- optimise your experience
- secure your user data and personal data
- improve our mobile apps
 
In some cases we will ask your permission before requesting access to this personal data in the context in which it is processed within the app.  The level of access may also depend on your device’s privacy settings which can be adjusted on the settings menu of your device.

